# Normalize all text to LF in the repo and on checkout, so the installer,
# scripts, and patches behave identically on Windows/macOS/Linux.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Patches must be preserved byte-for-byte (never EOL-converted) or `git apply`
# can fail / inject CRLF into source files.
*.patch -text

# Binary assets: never touch.
*.webp binary
